---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import ProcessSteps from '../components/ProcessSteps.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const title = "Headlight Restoration Fort Lauderdale | Mobile Service | Route95";
const description = "Professional headlight restoration in Fort Lauderdale. Remove yellowing, restore clarity, improve night visibility. Mobile service - we come to you! Call 754-215-2272";

const parentCategory = {
  href: `${base}car-detailing-services-fort-lauderdale/`,
  title: "Car Detailing Services"
};
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  h1="Headlight Restoration Fort Lauderdale"
  intro="Professional headlight restoration removes yellowing, oxidation, and haze from plastic headlight lenses, restoring clarity and dramatically improving night visibility."
  currentPage="/headlight-restoration-fort-lauderdale/"
  parentCategory={parentCategory}
>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Modern headlights use polycarbonate plastic lenses that deteriorate from UV exposure. In Fort Lauderdale, our intense sun causes headlight yellowing and hazing faster than almost anywhere else. What starts as slight haziness becomes severe oxidation that blocks up to 80% of your headlight output.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Yellowed headlights aren't just ugly—they're dangerous. Reduced light output means you can't see as far at night, and other drivers can't see you as well. Many vehicles fail safety inspections due to cloudy headlights. Replacement headlight assemblies cost $200-$1,000 or more per side.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We restore headlight clarity through wet sanding and polishing, then apply UV-protective clear coat to prevent future yellowing. Our mobile service brings professional headlight restoration directly to your Fort Lauderdale location for a fraction of replacement cost.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Much Does Headlight Restoration Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Professional headlight restoration in Fort Lauderdale costs $75 to $125 for both headlights.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Standard restoration of moderately hazed headlights falls at the lower end. Severely yellowed, heavily oxidized, or physically damaged lenses requiring extensive wet sanding cost more. The price includes UV-protective clear coat application.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">How Long Does Headlight Restoration Take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Headlight restoration takes 30 to 60 minutes for both headlights depending on the level of oxidation.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Lightly hazed lenses restore quickly. Severely yellowed headlights require multiple stages of wet sanding before polishing, which takes longer. The clear coat needs a few minutes to cure before driving.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Why Headlight Restoration Matters</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Cloudy headlights reduce your light output by up to 80%. That's the difference between seeing a hazard 300 feet ahead versus 60 feet—at highway speeds, that's stopping distance.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Problems caused by oxidized headlights:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Severely reduced night visibility</li>
          <li>Other drivers can't see you as well</li>
          <li>Vehicle looks older and poorly maintained</li>
          <li>May fail safety inspection</li>
          <li>Decreased resale value</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Fort Lauderdale's UV index averages 7-10 year-round—extreme levels that break down headlight plastic rapidly. Even new cars show headlight hazing within 2-3 years without protection.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-6">Our Headlight Restoration Process</h2>
        <ProcessSteps steps={[
          { title: "Masking", description: "We tape off the paint surrounding the headlights to protect your vehicle's finish during the sanding process." },
          { title: "Wet Sanding", description: "Starting with coarse grit and progressing to fine, we wet sand the lens to remove the oxidized layer and any pitting or scratches." },
          { title: "Compound Polishing", description: "We use cutting compound to remove sanding marks and begin restoring optical clarity to the lens surface." },
          { title: "Fine Polish", description: "A finishing polish brings the lens to crystal clarity, removing all haze and restoring the smooth, optically clear surface." },
          { title: "UV Clear Coat", description: "We apply a UV-protective clear coat that shields the bare plastic from sun damage, extending the restoration for 2-3 years." }
        ]} />
      </section>
    </div>

    <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Headlight Restoration Quick Facts</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-[#c9a227] font-bold">$</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">$75-$125 for both</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">30-60 minutes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Crystal clear results</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">UV protection included</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-[#c9a227] mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Lasts 2-3 years</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-[#1e3a5f] rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Book Headlight Restoration</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
            Same-day appointments available throughout Fort Lauderdale.
          </p>
          <a href="tel:+17542152272" class="btn-accent w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            754-215-2272
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3a5f] mb-4">Related Services</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={`${base}trim-restoration-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Trim Restoration</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}chrome-polishing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Chrome Polishing</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}car-waxing-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Car Waxing</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}full-detail-fort-lauderdale/`} class="text-gray-600 hover:text-[#c9a227]">Full Detail</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>
